  "history": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "text": "/all group command chenck kar skte ho   kis group me hai sara kisne add kiya hai jisne group se nikala hai"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "text": "Yeh to possible hai ki group ka owner nei apne phone se group ko banaya ho ya koi aur user nei group ko invite karke add kiya ho. 🤔 Group ka owner apne phone se group ko banane ke liye /newgroup command ka use kar sakta hai. Jab koi user invite karke group mein join karta hai, toh voh group mein add ho jata hai. Agar koi user group se nikalta hai, toh voh group mein apne naam aur profile picture ko remove kar deta hai. Lekin, voh group se permanently nikalta hai, toh voh group ko join karne ke liye invite karne ki zaroorat nahi padti. 🤝 Tum apne phone ke settings mein group ke details check kar sakte ho, jahan se tumhe pata chalega ki group ka owner kisne banaya hai aur kisne invite karke join kiya hai. 😊"
    }
  ],
